300187983.Title: Summit Appliance 27 in. 12.6 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Counter Depth, Silver
300187983.Description: Made for us in Europe, the FF1511SSLHD comes with an attractive platinum cabinet and stainless steel doors with a left hand swing. Designer style handles complete the modern look. At less than 26 in. deep, it offers a generous 12.6 cu. ft. capacity for maximum storage in a convenient fit. Inside, the FF1511SSLHD utilizes frost-free operation for minimum user maintenance and a dual evaporator system for improved cooling. Adjustable glass shelves offer spill-proof storage while multiple door racks are ideal for keeping condiments in easy reach. A large clear crisper drawer is included for optimum produce storage. Additional features make the FF1511SSLHD a user-friendly choice. LED lighting in the side walls of the refrigerator offers an efficient and attractive view inside. This unit includes an innovative touch control system that lets you manage the refrigerator and freezer temperature with an intuitive digital thermostat. For added energy savings, it features a vacation setting. The open door alarm alerts with an audio and visual signal when the door is left ajar for over one minute. The FF1511SSLHD is ENERGY STAR certified to ensure an efficient and low cost performance. With its professional style, unique size, and innovative features, this model is a great choice for smaller kitchens with full storage needs.

205584082.Title: Whirlpool 14.3 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in White
205584082.Description: Fit all of your fresh and frozen favorites without sacrificing any space with this ENERGY STAR rated 28 in. wide Whirlpool top-freezer refrigerator with 14.3 cu. ft. capacity. Enjoy quiet cooling with its improved design. And with the easy-to-install optional icemaker (sold separately) you'll be sure to have plenty of ice close at hand. Color: White.

300159571.Title: Whirlpool 18 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Silver
300159571.Description: Always find a place for your fresh and frozen goods inside this Whirlpool 28 in. top-freezer refrigerator. It offers convenient storage options between its 18 cu. ft. capacity and spacious FLEXI-SLIDE bin, which moves horizontally to accommodate tall items. Bright LED interior lighting casts a natural light on the contents of your black, white or stainless steel top-freezer refrigerator, giving your food the spotlight. Plus, you can add the Whirlpool EZ Connect icemaker kit for easily-accessible ice.
